README.md — Responsive HTML/CSS Website using CSS Grid

# Federal University of Education, Olosoho – Responsive Website

This is a fully responsive multi-page HTML/CSS website for a fictional institution called **Federal University of Education, Olosoho**. Built using **CSS Grid**, the layout adapts beautifully across desktop, tablet, and mobile devices.

## 🔧 Features

- ✅ Responsive layout using CSS Grid
- ✅ Cross-browser compatible
- ✅ Semantic HTML5 elements
- ✅ Multiple pages (Home, About, News, Admissions, etc.)
- ✅ Accessible and mobile-friendly

## 🌐 Live Demo

